Sentencas: The thermal expansion of La0.4Y0.1Sr0.5MnO3 samples has been studied by dilatometry up to 1000-degrees-C in air leading to a coefficient value of 10.5x10(-6) K-1.
Titulo: THERMAL-EXPANSION AND ELECTRICAL-CONDUCTIVITY OF YTTRIA-SUBSTITUTED LANTHANUM STRONTIUM MANGANITES

Sentencas: Conductivity measurements, carried out in the same temperature range show no noticeable influence of the oxygen partial pressure, but the substitution of La for Y in La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 significantly modifies the electrical behaviour, which passes from a metallic to a semiconductive type.
Titulo: THERMAL-EXPANSION AND ELECTRICAL-CONDUCTIVITY OF YTTRIA-SUBSTITUTED LANTHANUM STRONTIUM MANGANITES

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient of such La for Y substituted materials is much closer to that of yttria stabilized zirconia used as the solid electrolyte in solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: THERMAL-EXPANSION AND ELECTRICAL-CONDUCTIVITY OF YTTRIA-SUBSTITUTED LANTHANUM STRONTIUM MANGANITES

Sentencas: From this view point, this material offers an advantage over La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 cathode materials.
Titulo: THERMAL-EXPANSION AND ELECTRICAL-CONDUCTIVITY OF YTTRIA-SUBSTITUTED LANTHANUM STRONTIUM MANGANITES
